All Implemented Interfaces:
IPSCmsComponent, IPSDbComponent, Cloneable
public class PSSlotTypeContentTypeVariantSet
extends PSDbComponentSet

This is variant slot collection class, which is a dependent class of the PSContentTypeVariant. This wrapps up a relationship between the parent CONTENTVARIANTS and the child RXSLOTCONTENT tables.
